*CHARMED* pets = NPCs<br>
<br>
*NPCs* have a 4 pet target limit.<br>
<br>
Thats what the point is, hence charmed pets can sometimes get problems.<br>
It's not ALWAYS an absolute though, I've seen my mage summoned pet, only one there, refuse to attack a mob. In that case its probably soem weird bug, mayeb pathing problems or some such *shrug*<br>
<br>
And I have SEEN PERSONALLY 12+ pets sock it to ONE xp mob and kill the target in about 10-15 seconds, WAY faster than groups of folk were doing.<br>
